{"tid":598152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有乜PVP game係好玩？想用嚟維繫同男朋友嘅感情","createTime":"2018-03-19T09:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T10:13:09.000Z","uid":125434,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"09d33f1b9c525bc2606147e3041afa8ca12cf7c1","tid":598152,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"之前同男朋友一齊玩魔獸世界真係好開心，我做法師喺背後噴水丶佢做戰士喺前面衝鋒陷陣。玩咗兩年一齊做任務一齊殺玩家，得閑無聊可以喺個世界度玩好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過呢個遊戲而家已經冇咩玩家，變哂質。<br />\n<br />\n自從少咗呢啲遊戲之後(或者呢啲遊戲少咗人玩之後)，我同男朋友嘅關係就差咗。我地無再一齊打機殺玩家，依加唔單止野都少講咗，直頭野都少扑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以推介一隻巴絲都會中意玩嘅Pvp遊戲？"},{"pid":"eea776a28bb81f7321bdcbc60f36bcf634093888","tid":598152,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"我都想搵啲 game 同女朋友玩"},{"pid":"b6031bdba5472081025a53246bec34c0e20a8f4b","tid":598152,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"試下玩屎眼<br />\n又會有另一種味道"},{"pid":"fbf05e4eeca60085a99b7ae0c9bfbf814baa1ceb","tid":598152,"uid":108311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"我都想搵啲女朋友同我打機"},{"pid":"879eb570bd1b5cb14075c04912827785262f6119","tid":598152,"uid":125657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"ps4岩唔岩?"},{"pid":"6304c808e6ce65b2d1e46bd80e97b3aa5d89bee8","tid":598152,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879eb570bd1b5cb14075c04912827785262f6119","tid":598152,"uid":125657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"ps4岩唔岩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"都可以，諗住買俾佢做生日禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73503bc2410809f953a4957260ec85aad7095a34","tid":598152,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p